room_title: Escape room "Saloon Shakedown" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
room_description: Y'all did it! You robbed the Copperhead Creek Bank... But you didn't skedaddle fast enough so now the Saloon owner stole your getaway plans and is blackmailing you. He is threatening to turn you into the Sheriff if you don't cut him in on the loot! Steal back your plans and track down your horses to get out of town before the Sheriff shows up to take y'all in...
